@startuml
actor Lecturer
actor Student
participant "React Client" as Client
participant "Express API" as API
participant "Submission Service" as Service
database PostgreSQL as DB
participant WebSocket as WS

Lecturer -> Client : Open submission
Client -> API : GET /api/submissions/:id
API -> Service : getSubmission()
Service -> DB : SELECT submission, exam, questions
DB --> Service : Full grading data
Service --> Client : Answers and correct answers

Lecturer -> Client : Add points and feedback
Client -> API : PATCH /api/submissions/:id/grade
API -> Service : gradeSubmission()
Service -> DB : UPDATE manual/final scores
Service --> Client : Graded submission

Lecturer -> Client : Publish results
Client -> API : PATCH /api/exams/:id/results/publish
API -> DB : Verify no pending grading
API -> DB : SET results_published = true
API -> WS : results_published event
WS --> Student : Real-time notification
Student -> Client : Open My Results
Client -> API : GET /api/submissions/my
API --> Client : Scores, answers and feedback
@enduml
